ORDER
The motion of Alton W. Wiley that he be appointed to represent defendant David Collins in the prosecution of this appeal is granted.
DORIS, J., did not participate.

attorneys: Dennis J. Roberts II, Atty. Gen., Stephen R. Famiglietti; Special Asst. Atty. Gen., for plaintiff.
Alton W. Wiley, Providence, for defendant.
casebody.head_matter:
STATE v. David COLLINS.
No. 80-3-C.A.
Supreme Court of Rhode Island.
Feb. 21, 1980.
Dennis J. Roberts II, Atty. Gen., Stephen R. Famiglietti; Special Asst. Atty. Gen., for plaintiff.
Alton W. Wiley, Providence, for defendant.
